Package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake

package fi.abo.kogni.soile2.datamanagement.datalake
The datalake package contains all functionality and classes concerned with handling the files in the datalake(s) be it the git datalake or the participant datalake. They also handle translation between the file stubs in git and the datalake files.
Author:
Thomas Pfau
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    DataLakeFile
    This is a wrapper for a File in the datalake.
    DataLakeResourceManager
    A Manager/Retriever for Files for which indicator files are stored in the git Repository.
    GitDataLakeFile
    This class encapsulates information on how files for individual Elements are stored.
    ParticipantDataLakeManager
    This class represents a DataLakeManager for data in projects.
    ParticipantFileResult
    A Participant File Result maps a large file that was a result of a task from the name the file was given in the task to the local file where it was stored.
    ParticipantFileResults
    This class maps the participant data folder (i.e. files stored for the participant) to the actual folder on disk.
